All I want is to kill myself. That's the only thing I truly truly want. I can say the only reason I'm still alive is because I don't want to inflict trauma on the people who don't know not to care about me, or out of habit, but no. The real reason is that depression indiscriminately eradicated all substantial motivation. It drip feeds me enough to survive, maybe a little bit more so I can't release myself by going insane, but beyond that nothing. The same reason I haven't killed myself is the same exact reason I could never bring myself to do homework.
